data.title: Are Bruce and Kris Jenner getting a divorce?
data.meta_description:
As of 2013, they are still happily married, even after over 20
years of marriage. What they'll do in the future remains unknown,
although in my opinion, I think a divorce is unlikely and out of
the question.

Are Kim Kardashian and kloeh kardashian sisters?

yes. and Rob is their full brother. Their parents are Kris Kardashian Jenner & Robert Kardashian. The 2 younger girls are half sisters of the above 4. Their mother is Kris Kardashian Jenner & their father is Bruce Jenner. And Bruce Jenner has 3 other boys (Brody Jenner is one...) and a daughter from a previous marriage
